{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/cafe-yang-wajib-kamu-kunjungi-kalau-kamu-ke-jepang-dan-korea/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Cafe yang Wajib Kamu Kunjungi Kalau Kamu ke Jepang dan Korea!","content":"<p>Sebagai anak muda, kita pasti suka banget nongkrong buat ngabisin waktu bareng temen atau bahkan ngerjain tugas di kafe. Terutama cewek, yang rata-rata sukanya <em>dessert </em>atau makanan manis. Apalagi kalau kafe yang didatangi punya dekorasi menarik dan tema yang unik. Wah, gemesh deh pokoknya. Nah, di Jepang dan Korea Selatan ada banyak kafe lucu yang bisa kamu kunjungin loh! Pastinya, <em>cafe-cafe</em> ini <em>instagram-worthy </em>banget untuk foto-foto. Nah, mumpung sebentar lagi liburan, berikut  <em>list </em>kafe yang wajib didatangi kalau kamu liburan ke Jepang atau ke Korea ya.</p>\n<h3>1. Shirohige&#8217;s Totoro Cream Puff Factory di Tokyo, Jepang.</h3>\n<p>Kafe satu ini cocok banget buat penggemar studio Ghibli, karena menyajikan <em>dessert </em>dan dekorasi kafe dari karakter Totoro. Pemilik kafe ini memang katanya sepupu dari salah satu <em>founder </em>dari studio Ghibli. Gak cuma penuh dengan pajangan karakter Totoro aja, tapi menu favorit yang ditawarkan dari kafe ini adalah <em>cream puff</em>-nya yang berbentuk Totoro. <em>Cream puff</em> ini punya bermacam-macam rasa yang berbeda, menyesuaikan dengan musim di Jepang, seperti <em>strawberry cream</em> untuk Januari sampai Juni dan <em>peach cream</em> dari Juli hingga September. Bahan untuk membuat <em>dessert</em> di kafe ini memang berasal dari alam langsung yang mengikuti musim panen dari buah-buahan yang dipakai. Untuk alamat dan info lebih lanjut bisa cek ke <em>website</em>: <a href=\"http://www.shiro-hige.com\">www.shiro-hige.com</a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_6961\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6961\" data-attachment-id=\"6961\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/cafe-yang-wajib-kamu-kunjungi-kalau-kamu-ke-jepang-dan-korea/attachment/2-31/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/2-18.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: explodingbelly.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: explodingbelly.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/2-18.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/2-18.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6961\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/2-18.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: explodingbelly.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-6961\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: explodingbelly.com)</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_6958\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6958\" data-attachment-id=\"6958\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/cafe-yang-wajib-kamu-kunjungi-kalau-kamu-ke-jepang-dan-korea/attachment/1-34/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/1-21.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: shiro-hige.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: shiro-hige.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/1-21.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/1-21.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6958\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/1-21.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: shiro-hige.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-6958\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: shiro-hige.com)</p></div>\n<p><strong>2. STYLENANDA Pink Hotel &amp; Pink Pool Café di Seoul, Korea.</strong></p>\n<p>Kafe bernuansa pink satu ini memang ditujukan buat cewek-cewek yang mau nongkrong habis belanja <em>make-up</em> dan baju. STYLENANDA sendiri merupakan brand yang menjual <em>make up</em> dan pakaian di Korea. Kafe minimalis ini merupakan <em>feature</em> baru untuk menambah daya tarik STYLENANDA di mata pengunjung. Sesuai namanya, tema dari<em> Pink Hotel</em> adalah hotel bernuansa pink yang di tiap lantainya memiliki tema masing-masing, seperti <em>bathroom, laundry room, bedroom</em> dan juga <em>swimming pool</em>. Menu khas dari kafe ini adalah <em>Cotton Candy Ice Cream </em>dan berbagai minuman kopi<em>. </em>Untuk info lebih lanjut cek website <a href=\"http://stylenanda.com/\">http://stylenanda.com/</a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_6967\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6967\" data-attachment-id=\"6967\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/cafe-yang-wajib-kamu-kunjungi-kalau-kamu-ke-jepang-dan-korea/attachment/4-30/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/4-19.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: Seoulsearching.net)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: Seoulsearching.net)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/4-19.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/4-19.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6967\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/4-19.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: Seoulsearching.net)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-6967\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: Seoulsearching.net)</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_6964\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6964\" data-attachment-id=\"6964\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/cafe-yang-wajib-kamu-kunjungi-kalau-kamu-ke-jepang-dan-korea/attachment/3-34/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/3-21.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: Seoulsearching.net)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: Seoulsearching.net)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/3-21.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/3-21.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6964\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/3-21.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: Seoulsearching.net)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-6964\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: Seoulsearching.net)</p></div>\n<h3>3. Owl Café di Tokyo, Jepang.</h3>\n<p>Kalau kafe kucing dan anjing uda terlalu <em>mainstream </em>buat kamu, coba dateng ke kafe satu ini yuk. Akiba Fukurou atau Owl café ini memperbolehkan kamu berinteraksi langsung dengan burung hantu. Binatang <em>nocturnal </em> yang bikin kita teringat dengan film Harry Potter ini emang ga biasa ya! Kapan lagi kamu bisa dikelilingi burung hantu lucu dan imut? Kafe ini di-<em>design </em>semaksimal mungkin supaya pengunjung bisa merasakan ‘<em>healing</em>’ dari penatnya kesibukan sehari-hari dengan menghabiskan waktu bersama burung hantu. Yang lebih menariknya lagi, burung hantu disini memiliki berbagai macam jenis dan punya <em>personality</em> masing-masing, loh! Untuk ke kafe ini kamu bisa naik kereta ke Akihabara. Lalu dari stasiun, jalan sekitar 5 menit ke 67 Kanda Neribeicho (disarankan pakai <em>map</em> ya!).</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_6970\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6970\" data-attachment-id=\"6970\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/cafe-yang-wajib-kamu-kunjungi-kalau-kamu-ke-jepang-dan-korea/attachment/5-25/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/5-17.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: timetravelturtle.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: timetravelturtle.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/5-17.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/5-17.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6970\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/5-17.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: timetravelturtle.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-6970\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: timetravelturtle.com)</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_6973\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6973\" data-attachment-id=\"6973\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/cafe-yang-wajib-kamu-kunjungi-kalau-kamu-ke-jepang-dan-korea/attachment/6-19/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/6-12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: timetravelturtle.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: timetravelturtle.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/6-12.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/6-12.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6973\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/6-12.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: timetravelturtle.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-6973\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: timetravelturtle.com)</p></div>\n<h3>4. Aoyama Flower Market Tea House, Tokyo, Jepang.</h3>\n<p>Kafe ini menyajikan berbagai jenis teh untuk dicoba, seperti lemon grass, spearmint dan rosemary. Ga hanya teh, Aoyama Flower Market Tea House juga menjual macam-macam bunga. Dekorasi yang bernuansa bunga-bunga ini, pasti bikin betah pengunjungnya. Karena, selain kita bisa foto-foto buat di <em>upload</em> di Instagram, makanan dan minuman yang ditawarkan juga enak dan pastinya cocok banget buat orang yang pengen ‘nge-teh cantik’. Kafe ini juga menyediakan menu bahasa inggris, jadi kamu gak perlu bingung ketika mau memesan. Website kafe: http://www.afm-teahouse.com/</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_6982\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6982\" data-attachment-id=\"6982\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/cafe-yang-wajib-kamu-kunjungi-kalau-kamu-ke-jepang-dan-korea/attachment/9-9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: Tokyosheapo.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: Tokyosheapo.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9-5.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6982\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9-5.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: Tokyosheapo.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-6982\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: Tokyosheapo.com)</p></div>\n<h3>5. Contoyner Café, Seoul, Korea Selatan.</h3>\n<p>Kalau kamu berencana untuk liburan ke Seoul di musim panas, jangan lupa untuk datang ke kafe ini ya. Contoyner adalah kafe yang juga menjual pigura mainan dari berbagai tokoh animasi maupun film di lantai dasarnya. Di lantai paling atas kita bisa menikmati minuman dan makanan yang kita pesan dari kafe sambil foto-foto. Dekorasi warna cerah kafe memberikan kesan ‘summer’ banget. Ditambah dengan hiasan balon-balon <em>inflatable </em>ukuran besar membuat kamu terlihat seperti mainan yang ada di rumah boneka. Kafe ini terletak di Hongdae, dekat dari Sangsu Station, Seoul.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_6976\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6976\" data-attachment-id=\"6976\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/cafe-yang-wajib-kamu-kunjungi-kalau-kamu-ke-jepang-dan-korea/attachment/7-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/7-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: wababa.asia)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: wababa.asia)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/7-8.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/7-8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6976\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/7-8.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: wababa.asia)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-6976\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: wababa.asia)</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_6979\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6979\" data-attachment-id=\"6979\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/cafe-yang-wajib-kamu-kunjungi-kalau-kamu-ke-jepang-dan-korea/attachment/8-11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/8-6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(Sumber: blog.naver.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(Sumber: blog.naver.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/8-6.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/8-6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6979\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/8-6.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: blog.naver.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-6979\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: blog.naver.com)</p></div>\n<p>Wah, asiknya yang bentar lagi mau liburan. Bagi kamu yang bakal ke Korea atau Jepang, semoga rekomendasi cafe ini membantu ya. Kan lumayan bisa nambah-nambahin feed yang bagus di Instagram. hehe. Buat yang belum ada rencana buat jalan-jalan ke Jepang atau Korea, list cafe ini bisa kamu tampung loh untuk rencana liburan selanjutnya. <em>Keep reading CIAYO Blog and stay wonderful! </em> CIAYO!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"1ef3c5dd-9b04-5881-a625-801355197516"}}}